GetMagVar

public static double GetMagVar(double lat,
                               double lng,
                               double h,
                               long time,
                               double[] field)
Computes magnetic variation.

Parameters:
lat - geodetic latitude (radians)
lng - geodetic longitude (radians)
h - height (km)
time - time (milliseconds since Epoch)
field - output fields (or null): B_r, B_th, B_phi, B_x, B_y, B_z
Returns:
magnetic variation (radians), West is positive N and E latitude and longitudes are positive, S and W negative.
